Output example.mp4

Set Width 1280
Set Height 720
Set Zoom 1
Set Framerate 30
Set Sound true

Goto https://continuouscoordination.org/
Sleep 1s
Scroll Down 500
Hover "body > main > section > ul > li:nth-child(1) > a > h2"
Sleep 250ms
Click "body > main > section > ul > li:nth-child(1) > a > h2"
Sleep 1s
Scroll Down 500
Sleep 1s
Scroll Up 500
